Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:01.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:03.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.58,0:00:05.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.89,0:00:08.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:11.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:13.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:14.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:16.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, Sango, Inuyasha\nand {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:18.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I command these brave warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:20.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I'll defeat Naraku\nwith my Smashing Top!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:24.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's time for the start of Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:12.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:13.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaaow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:18.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- We're tired, Brother!\N- We're tired, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:19.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:21.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:21.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaaow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:25.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Let's take a break, Brother!\N- Let's take a break, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:28.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Meow.\N- Miaaow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:29.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:41.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Why, {\i1}you....!{\i0}\N- Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, now what do you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That'll teach you to\ntry to eat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:56.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is {\i1}that....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:02.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You shouldn't take\nme too lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:04.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! We're leaving, Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:08.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ah!! Wait for me!\NDon't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:11.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Don't tell {\i1}me....{\i0}\N- {\i1}That's....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Great Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:15.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's gotta be, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:16.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the Great Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:17.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:18.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaaow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:22.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's the legendary\NGreat Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:36.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You see, I lost both my\nma and my {\i1}pa....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:38.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Poor {\i1}Shippo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:42.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm okay. I've\ngot my friends with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They seem like good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:48.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm more worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The world of humans is\ngoing through tough times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:53.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Especially now that\NI've met {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Same here! Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:15.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How is it that Shippo meets\ngirls at every town we visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:19.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's probably due to the one\nhe's always hanging around with!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you've been seeing a demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,of course we'll get rid of it\nfor you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:30.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It might take a while if it's\nhiding up in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:34.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, we are very well aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:37.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what about lodging\nduring that {\i1}time....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:38.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Feh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:41.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You may stay here as\nlong as you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:45.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And could we ask the young\nladies to take care of {\i1}us....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:49.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can certainly ask some young\nmaidens over to help at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And through the night, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:56.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're asking a bit much\nof our host, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, well! If it isn't Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:01.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:04.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From what I hear it's only a\nstupid little small-fry demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:07.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with\nthe Jewel shards,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:11.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:13.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why should I care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's leave this dump of a\nvillage and be on our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:18.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:19.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit! boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:25.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ka....Kagome! Why, {\i1}you....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:26.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit! boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:29.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit! boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are your friends always\nso {\i1}violent....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:37.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's because they're\nstill children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:41.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But don't worry!\NI keep things together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:42.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, we'll be off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:47.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't thank you enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:49.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you look after things here,\nyou hear me, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:50.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, {\i1}yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you going, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:55.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They don't need me to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:58.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, what happens if the\ndemon attacks the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:01.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're placing all our\nhopes in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I {\i1}know....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:06.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'll go take\na look around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:20.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:24.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if\NMizuki will like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:26.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course she will!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:34.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaaow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:35.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:36.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:36.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:37.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:37.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:41.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mustard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Meow.\N- Miaaow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:45.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell do you\nthink you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:48.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're fox demons and we\nhad the good fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to come across our hero,\nthe Master Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:50.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:51.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mustard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:53.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Meow.\N- Miaaow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? {\i1}Master....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These are the times when the\nworld of demons is in turmoil
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,with this demon Naraku showing up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:03.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and other demons are wreaking\nhavoc all they like!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:08.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because of that, our family\nof fox demons was attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The five of us got separated\nfrom our parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and now we're\nlooking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Meow.\N- Miaaow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:18.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And during all this we heard\nrumors of the Master Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:21.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We heard there was a group who\nbattles with the evil Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:26.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And among them is a fox demon\nwho is a great hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Meow!\N- Miaaow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:35.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm....{\i0} Well, I guess that\nwould be {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:39.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master! We'll work very hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Train us hard to be\nstrong like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:43.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Make us your disciples!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:44.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your underlings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:44.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:45.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaaow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, no! The stories\nabout you are legion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even though you're\na demon yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you have among your\nfollowers a {\i1}priestess....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:57.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon {\i1}slayer....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:58.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A holy {\i1}monk....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Namu Namu Namu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:01.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And a {\i1}half-demon....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:07.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the Great Shippo who\nleads such illustrious warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:13.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me? I {\i1}lead....a priestess....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon {\i1}slayer....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A {\i1}monk....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:19.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And a {\i1}half-demon....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:22.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:26.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is my retainer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:30.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the humans are my servants!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:37.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master! Teach us\none of your deadly moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You had a technique when you\nfought with Naraku, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:41.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A deadly {\i1}technique....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! You must mean this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:49.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fox Magic, Smashing Top!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:54.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well? Whacha think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:55.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:56.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:57.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mustard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:57.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:58.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaoww!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:08:59.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please don't make fun of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:02.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have a really\nincredible one, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An incredible {\i1}one....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:09.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A terrific one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:11.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something like, "Wink Star!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:12.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Think Hard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Bean Curd!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Incredible skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:17.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:20.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you talking about\nthe Wind Scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:21.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:22.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:25.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please teach us\nthat one, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:25.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mustard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:26.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:27.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaaow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0} Um....You, {\i1}see....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master! Please teach us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right. I get it.\NCan you wait here a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:38.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm capable, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:43.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:46.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:54.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it, Shippo?\NHas the demon showed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lend it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's....the{\i0} WIND SCAR!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:05.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,WIND SCAR....WIND {\i1}SCAR....{\i0}\NWIND {\i1}SCAR....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What on earth are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! How do you\ndo the Wind Scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:17.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to use the\NWind Scar, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:18.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:21.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to be a lot {\i1}stronger....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:26.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, no! You can't just\nswing it around like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen, you have a sensitive nose
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:32.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and can smell the flow of\nthe demonic aura, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:35.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, that's where you go,\N"Ga-ga-ga!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:38.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And then, like you're slicing\nthrough it, go "Zu-ba-ba!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:40.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ga-ga-ga? Zu-ba-ba?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:43.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah! Ga-ga-ga and zu-ba-ba!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:46.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't get the "ga-ga-ga" and\nthe "zu-ba-ba" part!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:48.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you don't get the "ga-ga-ga" or\nthe "zu-ba-ba" parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then you'll never get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:52.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's like {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ga-ga-ga!!! And zu-ba-ba!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:00.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See? Like that....Ack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, this is bad!\NI decimated it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:12.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shippo....! This....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:18.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Where'd he go?\NShoot! I got carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:23.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was stupid to think Inuyasha\nwould teach it to {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:26.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:28.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:29.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:36.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I....uh....{\i0} I was going to check\naround for that demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:40.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! And I thought I'd\ngive this to {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, my! It's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, so I'm going back\nto look for the demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so you should go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay. Be careful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:53.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:05.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-How long have\nyou been standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:09.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:14.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Listen, about the Wind {\i1}Scar....{\i0}\NI don't have {\i1}it....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was great, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:17.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:20.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Enchanting that human\ngirl so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wasn't exactly\nenchanting {\i1}her....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:26.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We fox demons have a long\ntradition of bewitching folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:29.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And we can't let the\nraccoon dog demons outdo us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:34.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, Master! Are you going to\ndo something awful to this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, not {\i1}really....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:39.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure Master Shippo has a\nterrific technique for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:42.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We wanna watch!\NWe wanna watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}J- Just what're these\nfox demons thinking?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Outta my way, you fox brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You creep! What do you\nthink you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:03.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This must be the demon who is\nterrorizing the village!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to get word to\NInuyasha right away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:09.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it! Do you know who\nyou're dealing with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:10.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the master famous\nthroughout the fox demon world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:15.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the one and only Master Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the one who should\nget out of his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:23.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Just be good and apologize!\N- If you don't, he'll getcha!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wonder at the power\nof Master Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:26.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be amazed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be amazed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey....why{\i0} are you holding onto me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:34.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah? Well, I guess\NI've gotta fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:36.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go get him, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:37.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:37.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:38.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaaow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:44.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on! I'm ready anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fox Magic! Anything to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:50.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:59.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, you little squirts!\NHow dare you make a fool of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ma....Master!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Little twerps!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow....{\i0} It looks like I got\naway from that {\i1}one....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! I {\i1}sense....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:18.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:18.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:19.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mustard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:19.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:20.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaoww!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:24.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you really the hero of the\nfox demons, Master Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:29.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well....yeah! I'm Shippo. No\ntwo ways about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you really are a\npowerful demon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well....yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:39.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you really have a\ndeadly technique, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:40.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh....huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then why did you run off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:43.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, you {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:44.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ah! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:48.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M-Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:56.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:57.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's the one you'll\nplay a trick on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please show us how\nwell you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:00.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We wanna see!\NWe wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:06.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There really is no need\nto enchant a human {\i1}girl....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:07.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:12.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're the hero of\nthe fox demons, Master Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:15.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:22.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I am! I am Shippo!\NNo question about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a lovely {\i1}smell....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,La-di-la-di-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why's this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:44.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why's this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:48.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ha, ha! Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Take that!\N- Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:52.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww!! That hurts! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, quit jumping {\i1}around....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mi....Mizuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:12.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mizuki....?{\i0} Are {\i1}you....are you....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:18.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shippo....{\i0}\NIt was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:22.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Good job! Good job!\N- Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:34.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Way to go!\N- Wow, she's a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:38.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Hey! Human girl!\N- Learned your lesson?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:47.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:48.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:51.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Way to go! Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:56.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah....M- Mizuki....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:01.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mustard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:02.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:03.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaoww!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:06.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:10.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This....wasn't much at {\i1}all....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:17.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once {\i1}again....{\i0}\nmy first love is {\i1}over....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:21.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good job! Way to go!\NDid you see that, little girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:32.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A little while ago you made a\nfool of me with that cheap trick
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:35.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but this time we're gonna\nsettle things properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:37.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:37.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mustard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:38.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:39.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaoww!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:42.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up! What's with\nthis "mustard" stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:45.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, if you think you\nwant to apologize to {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:51.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! What? What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If it hadn't been for you\nshowing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd....I'd....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:18:00.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You're really going\nto fight me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:03.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd never have had to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:07.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Mizuki wouldn't hate me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:08.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You {\i1}little....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:23.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And next, I'll see to you {\i1}guys....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:30.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You little twerp!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:46.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see it!\NA flow of demonic power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the Master's\ndeadly technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:53.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the Wind Scar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:55.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:56.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaaow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not the Wind Scar!\N{\i1}It's....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:06.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the Heart Scar!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:12.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's even more incredible\nthan the Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:15.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ow, ow! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you {\i1}little....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Heart Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow.! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:23.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You all join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah! Come on, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:32.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heart....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heart....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:34.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heart....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:39.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! No! I can't take it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:44.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were terrific, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:45.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mustard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:46.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:47.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miaaow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:50.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've learned a great deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your fox demon technique:\nthe Heart Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:54.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hope you'll allow us\nto use it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:55.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:58.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now we have much more\nconfidence in ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:00.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can now go looking\nfor our mother and father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:05.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a short friendship,\nbut we'll never forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:10.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so, we're off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My first love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:34.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:38.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, that little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:41.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The next time I see him,\NI'll whomp him good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:46.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:48.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ackkkk! That stings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:52.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, another one vanquished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:57.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:58.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Namu Amida {\i1}Butsu....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:04.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you so much! You've\ndone us a great service.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:08.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not at all. It really wasn't\nsuch a dangerous demon anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:12.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry we finished\nso {\i1}quickly....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:13.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:15.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's up, Shippo?\NSomething wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:16.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:20.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you saying you're the one\nwho fixed that demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:23.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares about that foolishness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:23.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um....Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:36.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bleh! Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:44.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Shippo! What've you done?\NWhat's she so mad about, heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:45.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, {\i1}you....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Heart Scar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:51.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yow, ow, ow! Hey!\NWhadaya think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:53.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's all that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.09,0:21:54.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:57.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Another test from the\ngreat Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Heart Scar!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:05.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mizuki!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:48.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're supposed to find\nthe den of demon women...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:50.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but Miroku is flirting with\nwomen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:51.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say {\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.48,0:23:52.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there really nothing\nbetween you and Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:54.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:57.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you two were alone at Mt. Hakurei,\nnothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:23:59.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a thing to ask, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.65,0:24:01.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku and I don't have\nthat kind of relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:04.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think Miroku likes you, Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:09.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Trap of the Cursed Wall Hanging"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.86,0:24:11.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so reliable\nin times of trouble.
